| dead-url        = no
}}</ref>2009年3月，获得Dr. Dobb's杰出编程奖。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.drdobbs.com/cpp/dr-dobbs-2009-excellence-in-programming/215900307|title=Dr. Dobb's 2009 Excellence in Programming Award|last=Erickson|first=Jonathan|date=15 March 2009|website=DR. Dobb's|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719061146/http://www.drdobbs.com/cpp/dr-dobbs-2009-excellence-in-programming/215900307|archive-date=2019-07-19|access-date=5 January 2019|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.drdobbs.com/cpp/dr-dobbs-2009-excellence-in-programming/215900307 |title="Dr. Dobb's 2009 Excellence in Programming Award" |accessdate=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2019-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719061146/http://www.drdobbs.com/cpp/dr-dobbs-2009-excellence-in-programming/215900307 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，宣布退出C++世界。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://scottmeyers.blogspot.fr/2015/12/good-to-go.html |title="} // good to go" |accessdate=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2018-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222190545/http://scottmeyers.blogspot.fr/2015/12/good-to-go.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

